      <b data-is-speakable>Previously Unseen Photos Of Michelle Obama Illuminate 'Chasing Light'</b>   <b data-is-speakable>Official White House photographer Amanda Lucidon's new book collects scenes featuring the former first lady — "one of the most genuine and compassionate and thoughtful people" she'd ever met.</b>
