    <div id="res560467025" class="bucketwrap bookedition">
      <h6><a href="https://www.npr.org/books/titles/560466866/chasing-light-michelle-obama-through-the-lens-of-a-white-house-photographer">Chasing Light</a></h6>
   <p>Michelle Obama Through the Lens of a White House Photographer</p>   <p class="author">by <a href="https://www.npr.org/books/authors/560467014/amanda-lucidon"><span>Amanda Lucidon</span></a></p>   <div class="bookinfo">
            <p>Hardcover, 222 pages <span class="pipe">|</span></p>      <a href="#" class="purchase" data-metrics='{"category":"Ecommerce","action":"Click purchase book"}' >purchase</a>      <div class="ecommercepop">
                  <div class="ecomm_body">
                        <button class='btn-close'>close overlay</button>            <h3>Buy Featured Book</h3>
